  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a missionary, you go to spread your message to a wicked man. He, however, wants to play a card game with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/5ec029691c34d9635430eb39e2cd42b3.poster.avif?t=1739261833\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/5ec029691c34d9635430eb39e2cd42b3.webm?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/5ec029691c34d9635430eb39e2cd42b3.mp4?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>HOW ABOUT WE PLAY A GAME?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Psychological Horror Card Game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/48676fe2cc09e9760ae5a89dff228122.poster.avif?t=1739261833\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/48676fe2cc09e9760ae5a89dff228122.webm?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/48676fe2cc09e9760ae5a89dff228122.mp4?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Immerse yourself in a haunting PSX-style retro world, or will it consume you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/29f9eada06325a384d71020dd55e9880.poster.avif?t=1739261833\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/29f9eada06325a384d71020dd55e9880.webm?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/29f9eada06325a384d71020dd55e9880.mp4?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exprimental and Psychological:</strong> A fresh take on psychological horror Cardgame.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense Card Battles:</strong> Rely on <strong>luck</strong> and <strong>strategy</strong> to barely survive fierce battles and acquire new cards to beat the Wicked Man's game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short & Perfect for a Weekend:</strong> Designed to be completed in a weekend, offering a concise yet impactful experience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deckbuilding Mechanics:</strong> Customize your deck to suit your playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multilingual Support:</strong> Enjoy the game in your preferred language with subtitle support for 15 different languages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric Horror:</strong> Immerse yourself in a chilling horror atmosphere with visuals and a hauntingly beautiful soundtrack. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story-Rich Experience:</strong> Dive into a captivating narrative that unfolds as you progress, with  intriguing characters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High Replayability:</strong> Challenge yourself endlessly in Unlimited Mode, offering fresh runs and limitless card battles. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Leaderboards: </strong>Compete with players worldwide and see how your scores rank on the Steam leaderboards. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Achievement Support: </strong>Unlock a variety of achievements as you master the game, adding extra layers of challenge and reward.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a missionary, you go to spread your message to a wicked man. He, however, wants to play a card game with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/5ec029691c34d9635430eb39e2cd42b3.poster.avif?t=1739261833\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/5ec029691c34d9635430eb39e2cd42b3.webm?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/5ec029691c34d9635430eb39e2cd42b3.mp4?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>HOW ABOUT WE PLAY A GAME?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Psychological Horror Card Game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/48676fe2cc09e9760ae5a89dff228122.poster.avif?t=1739261833\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/48676fe2cc09e9760ae5a89dff228122.webm?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/48676fe2cc09e9760ae5a89dff228122.mp4?t=1739261833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Immerse yourself in a haunting PSX-style retro world, or will it consume you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063960/extras/29f9eada06325a384d71020dd55e9880.poster.avif?t=1739261833\"